data.title: Private Equity
data.meta_description: Get in touch with the CF Private Equity team.
data.text:
We love working with journalists to share our insights. Send us a note and our PR firm will be in touch.

If you prefer to reach out via telephone, you may contact Emily Roy at Prosek Partners directly at (646) 818-9232.

We are interested in partnering with investment managers where we have an alignment of interests. Fill out the form here, and we will circle back with you on how best to proceed.

Have questions about Commonfund in general? Use the button below to call our general line at (888) 823-6246.

Already an investor with us and have questions on your account? Call our Investor Services Team directly at (888) 823-3863.
